{"tid":1030671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］臭雞姐上水做乜撚嘢","createTime":"2019-02-21T06:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T03:00:05.000Z","uid":73267,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf8219e6706ce278b59d5cd91e7af98488e31af","tid":1030671,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"「喺呢個事之後<br />\n如果你仲紅得起<br />\n咁，我真係恭喜你啊」<br />\n<br />\n唔好再出嚟獻世啦<br />\n偷人電話咁撚陰質嘅嘢都做得出<br />\n入返你老母個閪到繼續扭屎忽啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kKH7P6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kKH7P6.png&h=04a8bfa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e59c2ee334577143d958f7c84864a1a08ea05541","tid":1030671,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"自左首未?"},{"pid":"934490b740b16d6748242becddc9ff3ab3825c64","tid":1030671,"uid":83094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:14:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6baf08dabed7ff75b0694fccc4c50cd073316858","tid":1030671,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33b483d1bf32edb81bb910f9ecbc32ceb52a036d","tid":1030671,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"小偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76184720bb6d26b58e82358bfcf041c4274fe676","tid":1030671,"uid":73267,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9ihWTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9ihWTv.png&h=66c8763c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，一起去愛！？<br />\n一起去偷就有你份<br />\n呢個時候係到post呢啲嘢做咩啫<br />\n話比人聽你好堅強？<br />\n之前唔係成日出story發放正能量<br />\n成個人生教練咁㗎咩<br />\n收皮啦 好撚虛偽啊"},{"pid":"62